{"tid":1880812,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[耶青] 支爆十災，全黨死清光","createTime":"2020-02-15T06:37:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-15T13:07:05.000Z","uid":56052,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0b736eacffa5a14a33e243584c69082081561807","tid":1880812,"uid":56052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T06:37:41.000Z","msg":"我地重溫一下聖經舊約嘅十災 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1.  血災<br />\n尼羅河的清水全變成血水<br />\n<br />\n2. 蛙災<br />\n大量青蛙遍佈埃及<br />\n<br />\n3. 虱災<br />\n埃及人身上佈滿虱子<br />\n<br />\n4. 蠅災<br />\n蒼蠅肆虐<br />\n<br />\n5. <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">疫災</span></span><br />\n家畜感染瘟疫死亡。 ( <span style=\"color: red;\">2019 支那非洲豬瘟</span>)<br />\n<br />\n6. 疹災<br />\n成人長出起泡的疹子<br />\n<br />\n7. <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">雹災</span></span><br />\n天降冰雹 (<span style=\"color: red;\">2020湖北冰雹，氣溫急降更有阻病毒生存</span>)<br />\n<br />\n8. <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">蝗災</span></span><br />\n蝗蟲佈滿埃及 (<span style=\"color: red;\">2020 西亞蝗蟲扺達支那邊境</span>)<br />\n<br />\n9. 夜災<br />\n三天三夜不見太陽<br />\n<br />\n10. <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">長子之死</span></span><br />\n所有埃及家庭的長子以及埃及一切頭生的牲畜死亡 (<span style=\"color: red;\">2020 武漢肺炎</span>)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">當天滅中共成為事實，香港人革命就係每個人嘅職責</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔好放棄，唔好輕鬆，革命非一朝一夕，只有堅持先有出路<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3Ke44tO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3Ke44tO.jpg&h=cce5b8e3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0218feadb3359407fad2b50f28137a903173a003","tid":1880812,"uid":56052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T06:43:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9a2539e3b831566c77e9eaddb0039ef6cf16bce","tid":1880812,"uid":56052,"like":